Package Inventory

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddPartController
    AddPartController allows you to add a Part in the UI and handles input.
    AddProductController
    AddProductController allows you to add a Product in the UI and handles input.
    AlertMessage
    Alert will create alerts for the application to prevent runtime errors
    InHouse
    InHouse extends Part where it will be given a machine id
    Inventory
    Inventory is the model, it will hold Parts and Products
    Main
    Main class extends application, this application can be extended to read input from a database that can hold a large database of Parts and Products.
    MainController
    MainController is called by main and begins the app, buttons and inital user input will be handled by this class.
    ModifyPartController
    ModifyPartController allows you to modify a Part in the UI and handles input.
    ModifyProductController
    ModifyProductController allows you to modify a Product in the UI and handles input.
    OutSourced
    OutSourced extends Part where it will be given a company name
    Part  
    Product
    Product Class is part of the model
